defaultRECOMMENDATION: 
defaultM
defaultandatory requirement to have best available 
defaultdesign and 
defaulttechnology 
defaultin HGVs to eliminate blind areas
default firstly focussing on 
defaultdesign for 
defaultdirect vision (lower cabs and clear doors) and secondly focusing on technology primarily that which automatically controls the vehicle eg ABS, vehicle
default departure warnings and sensors
default when danger of collision occurs.
