default3.11
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultExisting cycle lanes are positioned on the left side of the highway. Over 50% of cyclist deaths 
defaultare 
defaultcaused by left turning 
defaultvehicles. Much danger is presented to those in cycle lanes
default 
defaultby motor vehicles entering cycle lanes and advanced stop boxes whilst driving and parking
default generating fear and conflict
default.  
