default3.21
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe President of the Institution of Highways Engineers at the end of June 2012 called for a ban on HGVs on motorw
defaultays on Sundays.
default 
defaultHGVs are banned in Dublin, Delhi, Paris and Dhaka. A lorry ban occurred in London during the 2 weeks of the Olympics. Not only were no adverse effects obvious but also it was widely reported that London was a much safer, more attractive and
default efficient place to be and through which to travel. 
